Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:05.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So, we met each other… {ep12}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.84,0:00:07.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,…when we were kids. {ep12}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.93,0:00:12.85,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You knew who I was from the beginning, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:14.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.73,0:00:21.34,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,When you came to the library, I was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.78,0:00:25.70,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I was happy to see that the boy\Nfrom those days had come back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:31.66,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,But I realized soon enough that you didn't remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.24,0:00:36.21,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Yet, you became friends with me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:40.12,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,You treated me as kindly as a girl you had met for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.63,0:00:43.58,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,You introduced me to many friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:46.98,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Then I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:52.45,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I couldn't decide if I wanted you\Nto remember or remain unaware…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:00:55.88,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,…of what I was like back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:31.86,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(957.273,411.75)}Episode 13
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:31.86,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(965.455,724.5)}Garden of Memories
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:37.09,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,“Those who pursue truth must not be arrogant.”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:43.22,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,“Just because it can't be proven scientifically, you must not laugh at miracles.”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:47.73,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,“You must not deny your eyes the beauty of this world.”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:51.76,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Those were my father's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:54.86,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Why was I named Kotomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:58.28,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Look around, Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:06.75,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,This world is composed of countless harps that cannot be seen by the naked eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.31,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Koto would be Japanese for harp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:11.00,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Koto as in Kotomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:19.51,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,The world is filled with harps,\Nand each one plays a different tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:25.52,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,All those tunes intertwine with each other,\Nand a unique melody is born.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:29.15,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,That's why the world is so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:33.06,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,It's Father's bad habit to try to speak eloquently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:37.49,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,The most important things are always very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:40.01,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Your name is Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:42.78,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Spelled with three cute hiragana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:49.12,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You're Father and Mother's very, very precious treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.65,0:03:55.13,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,My house, the yard, Father, and Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:59.60,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,That's what my world was composed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:20.17,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:22.44,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:25.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was playing and wandered in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:27.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.07,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:31.35,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,You spell Kotomi with three hiragana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:33.16,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,When you call me, call me Kotomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.57,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh my, we have a cute guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:41.59,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I was alone at school…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:47.85,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,…because I read books my classmates wouldn't and thought of things they wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:55.61,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,But this boy, Okazaki Tomoya, seemed a little different from the boys I knew at my school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.02,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,A doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:05:01.41,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Yes. I want a doll of a bear for my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:06.13,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I see. Okay. I'll find you the cutest bear then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:09.56,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,To be honest, I didn't mind what I got as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:17.57,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,A book said girls usually wanted dolls, so I only copied that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:19.42,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:24.33,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,What? Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.33,0:05:26.56,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,It's a business trip that came up suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:30.21,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Both Father and Mother have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:36.27,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,But we promised! We promised that you'd both be here for my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.08,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Even Tomoya-kun will be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:42.05,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,He said he'll come with his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:44.54,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I have the food for the birthday party made already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:48.85,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,When Tomoya-kun and his friends come, eat it with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:51.30,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,You two are liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.04,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I hate you both!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.04,0:05:53.12,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:57.02,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I know! We'll pick up your bear on the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:59.11,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,A really big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:00.58,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,We'll ship it to you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:03.63,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I don't need it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:06.99,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I hate you both!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:09.31,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:14.56,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Nobody came on my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:19.11,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,The housemaid got sick, too, so I was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:23.63,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,And, Tomoya-kun didn't show up, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:38.21,Default,Man,0,0,0,,May I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:43.35,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I was told that I can't let people I don't know inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:46.84,Default,Man,0,0,0,,You haven't heard what happened to your father and mother yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:51.31,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,He explained everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:57.61,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,How the plane Father and Mother were on\Nmalfunctioned in midair and sank into a distant ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:02.96,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,How a very important paper sank with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:07.61,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,How there might be a spare copy in Father's study.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:14.58,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,How important the paper was to the world, and therefore, how it had to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:18.00,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Go home! Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:20.73,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,This person had to be a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:24.14,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,He was here to take away\Nsomething important of Father's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:26.04,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,That was what I had thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:32.10,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'll become a very good girl from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:34.31,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I will never say anything selfish anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:36.84,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'll study a lot, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:40.31,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'll read lots of books and become smart, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:43.04,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,So dear god, I beg you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:45.69,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Please bring Father and Mother back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:51.02,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Please. Bring them back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:08:00.12,Default-alt,News,0,0,0,,{\fscx95}The crash occurred as they were flying to the United States for a special conference, having advanced their schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:02.04,Default-alt,News,0,0,0,,A search party has been already sent out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:05.55,Default-alt,News,0,0,0,,However, judging from the site of crash,\Nthe chances of survival for the missing people are slim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:09.79,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:11.52,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Mother, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:15.97,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.56,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:19.82,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'll be a good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:24.27,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'll be a good girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:28.47,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'll be a good girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:33.02,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Father's study was the last place I went into.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:40.37,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I was always told not to,\Nbut that was the only place left to search.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:50.07,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I figured that had to be the important paper\Nthe bad guy was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:55.97,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I believed that it was that which caused Father and Mother to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:09:00.12,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It was wrong for something like that to be so important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:05.04,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I didn't care about the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:10.44,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,All I wanted was Father and Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:39.63,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:42.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are these all articles about the crash?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:47.77,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I think I started this as a way of atoning for my sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.39,0:09:55.78,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I started to collect scraps of all the newspaper articles that talked about Father and Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:10:05.04,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,But that didn't feel enough to me, so I began\Ncollecting pages from books that mentioned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:09.04,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Then, I studied a lot…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:13.18,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,…because I wanted to follow\Nin the footsteps of Father and Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:21.56,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Father and Mother were trying to express the foundation of this world using the most beautiful words.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:25.81,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It's something that must be told to everyone in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:28.97,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It's something nobody else can copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:31.29,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Not even me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:41.05,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,But if I don't do it… god won't\Nforgive me for burning the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:43.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kotomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:47.20,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I don't want to experience anything that sad again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:50.04,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose someone I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.61,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Please go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:00.31,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,I see, so you heard the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:02.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sensei, is Kotomi present today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.31,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,She called saying she'll be absent for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:13.15,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Okazaki-kun, do you know that\NIchinose-san has an offer to go study abroad? {ep12}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:14.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Study abroad? {ep12}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:19.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's a program where a student with outstanding grades can study at a college in the US.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:23.53,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's up to the individual to choose whether to come back to Japan after that or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:27.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ichinose-san wasn't very enthusiastic about it couple days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:32.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,but today over the phone she said that she would accept the offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:39.87,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So Kotomi-chan has always remembered you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:44.63,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah. Although I only vaguely remember those times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:48.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll visit Kotomi's place again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:49.56,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Then I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:52.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You should go to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:55.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Pass along the details to Kyou and Fujibayashi for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:57.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:06.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kotomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.56,0:12:39.11,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:45.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I told you to go to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:48.05,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The third period became a study hall.{ep12}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:50.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I couldn't get it off my mind.{ep12}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:52.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're raking the yard?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:56.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, I wanted to do whatever I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:13:00.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Both Kyou-chan and Ryou-chan were saying the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.04,0:13:02.80,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,“Let's do whatever we can.”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.93,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are they planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:07.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Give me a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:09.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:14.56,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, did the hint make it too easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:17.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kotomi's birthday is this coming Saturday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:20.82,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. Today's Tuesday, so in four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.83,0:13:25.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Pass the word to those two: “Let's do our best.”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:27.10,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:34.79,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But, I think Okazaki-san is the only person in the world who can bring Kotomi-chan back to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:38.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're being overdramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:39.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:03.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It'll never get done at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:08.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I may have to get some tools together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:10.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll continue tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:15.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Good night, Kotomi. {ep12}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kotomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:24.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're up there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:05.15,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, this used to be a flowerbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:11.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's gotten a little better, but I won't finish in time at the pace I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:14.19,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I have to do something about this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:21.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I guess I have to get all the necessary tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This looks like more work than I'd expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:30.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:33.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:37.01,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What are you loitering around here for? {ep12}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:38.04,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Shopping. {ep12}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:40.83,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You're wealthier that I'd thought. {ep12}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:44.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's the money I had saved up\Ntowards moving out of my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:54.76,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:59.57,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,We meant to give it to Kotomi as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.94,0:16:07.81,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,We contacted the senpai who left the violin behind, and we officially received ownership.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:17.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,{\fscx100}Talking to Nishina-san, she said it should get properly tuned,\Nso we were on our way to an instrument shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:22.17,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Let me tell you, it's 100% the biker's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:27.38,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,If I'd had a metal pipe in my hand,\NI would have smacked him along with his bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:29.57,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:32.71,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,This wouldn't have happened if we had been more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:35.12,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You two are taking it too hard on yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:36.76,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,It's about time you stop brooding over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:40.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's right. Nothing will come from sitting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.07,0:16:41.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's head over to an instrument shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:47.94,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Being this damaged, it'd be cheaper to buy a new one rather than fixing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:52.51,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey, you're using our situation to your advantage and trying to make a sale off of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:55.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Stop, Kyou. That's too rude of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.67,0:16:57.52,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,He's right, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:17:00.52,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, it's something really important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:03.19,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Can you do something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:08.59,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,He wouldn't accept it in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:11.44,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,He was definitely trying to take advantage of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.44,0:17:15.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But it's true that a new one would be cheaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.23,0:17:18.53,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,It has to be this violin for Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.01,0:17:25.56,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Let's try another shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:28.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We can't give up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.49,Default,Man,0,0,0,,If you're so adamant about it…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:41.35,Default,Man,0,0,0,,But, even if it is repairable,\NSaturday is an impossible date.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:45.32,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Then, how long will it take?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:48.53,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Well, it's a little tough to make a guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:51.28,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Somewhere between a month and half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:52.30,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,That's way too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.63,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Cut it down to two days, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:56.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You should stay quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:18:02.47,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Also, when it comes back, there's no guarantee that it'll play with the sound it used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:05.19,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,God, this is pissing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:06.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.71,0:18:09.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We're lucky enough that he accepted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:13.13,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,How much do you think the repair fee will cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:15.51,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:18.10,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,If it comes down to it, we'll collect money at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:22.14,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you're the organizer, it might turn into blackmail rather than a collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:30.30,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,It was so much fun up until a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:33.06,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Why didn't things turn out well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:40.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I wonder if Kotomi-chan is still at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:47.56,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey, you made quite a bit of progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:52.07,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,You're amazing to have done all of this alone, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:56.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Not at all. I'm not sure if I'll make it for Saturday or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:02.14,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Kotomi! You're up there, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.48,0:19:03.58,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:05.09,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Kotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:08.93,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Onee-chan, you shouldn't shout at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:11.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're disturbing the neighbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:21.60,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san, may we help, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.63,0:19:25.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thanks, but it's already late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:28.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you arrive home late, your parents will be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:37.66,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,All right. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:44.51,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please don't push yourself too hard, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:48.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I know. Once I get the tools together, I'll go home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:52.06,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Good night, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:53.44,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:08.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,All right, I guess I'll do some more work. {ep12}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:25.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's likely buried here are my memories as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:29.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is Kotomi asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:32.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I hope she's not having any nightmares.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:37.88,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Maybe what I'm doing right now is all a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:42.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,When that happens, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:48.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,When that happens, will I be able to bear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:51.87,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.53,0:21:00.36,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:05.03,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Just like Nagisa said, you're still working.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:12.00,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Please let us help you. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:14.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Okay. Only thirty minutes, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:15.92,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.92,0:21:23.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's right. There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:26.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:42.49,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:44.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:48.11,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I thought I just saw the curtain move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:58.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's keep working.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:00.10,Default,All,0,0,0,,Yeah.
