Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:09.66,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(981.818,384.75)\c&HFFFFFF&\be2\4c&H000000&\3c&H454845&\bord3.15}Episode 14
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.03,0:23:43.76,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Day before yesterday I saw a rabbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:45.38,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,and yesterday a deer,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.08,0:23:47.51,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,and today, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.26,0:23:53.82,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I always remembered the boy who wandered into the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.52,0:23:59.78,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I really, really liked that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:04.24,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,He was my only friend…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.21,0:24:08.81,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,…so I kept waiting for him.
